{"tid":2107193,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛人亦要花氣力 冇力冇勇氣了","createTime":"2020-07-13T16:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T12:57:04.000Z","uid":183576,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"45e2154230eb0ce0d37db9c3234eac0b006feda5","tid":2107193,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:53:31.000Z","msg":"人大左，好驚會再愛上/依賴一個人<br />\n一旦依賴後發現冇可能發展、甚至冇可能熟絡 咁就碌柒，連遠遠守望嘅資格都冇<br />\n<br />\n本身已經同自己講要心如鐵石、唔好幻想，但鬼叫自己衰on9沉左船，一沉沉左半年就返唔到轉頭 開始好多傷春悲秋<br />\n好想要返個密封罩封死自己 冇感情就冇期望冇傷心<br />\n<br />\n反正個個被我鍾意嘅都會離開<br />\n咁點解仲要去勉強自己一次次踩入火坑受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13389cf2b3de8260a98ab2f42f7ac798dd3c692e","tid":2107193,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:54:11.000Z","msg":"望人大咗望到驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8208f806a3f0f9ce53c2a768277e519a44920a76","tid":2107193,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f328524900e352893b4e99957826c508dc4f9ad","tid":2107193,"uid":86643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:58:21.000Z","msg":"True<br />\nSad"},{"pid":"1a42610d77015440a84f6904b2e99e2cba0e31d6","tid":2107193,"uid":287099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"我想係 鍾意左半年 <br />\n對方一直都知<br />\n然後幾個星期前 派左卡比我 連朋友都做唔到"},{"pid":"990e5a0d357f832572a1b21808bf7232102d6dde","tid":2107193,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8208f806a3f0f9ce53c2a768277e519a44920a76","tid":2107193,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T17:00:42.000Z","msg":"bb唔好入來刺激我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628